{"tid":1754591,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］洪興山雞重出江湖","createTime":"2019-11-25T09:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T09:38:38.000Z","uid":308567,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4a64221ba9596213c1cf5ccf215b995ece0470d0","tid":1754591,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:12:41.000Z","msg":"小春子🖕你又唔撚洗兇人嘅🤬定係知自己身有💩記者都係想訪問下你🎤點撚解你仲未俾人拉🚓👮🏻&zwj;♂政協委員犯法唔洗拉㗎👨🏻&zwj;⚖️ 政協委員大撚哂㗎🤔柒頭🤡你可以十萬個放心❤️小編一定幫你推撚到上火星🚀惡？🤬<br />\n<br />\n#人一藍腦便殘<br />\n#如果大家幫小編一齊大力SHARE就好喇<br />\n#集合大家力量<br />\n<br />\n根據《選舉管理委員會（選舉程序）（區議會）規例》，任何人於投票日在並無准許的情況下，在任何投票站內拍影片、拍照、錄音或錄影，即屬犯罪，可處最高罰款5,000港幣及監禁6個月<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5BohRyB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5BohRyB.jpg&h=9d92d88e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fNXKwyB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfNXKwyB.jpg&h=8af971fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/103874037623208/posts/151422459535032?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F103874037623208%2Fposts%2F151422459535032%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=622287fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/103874037623208/posts/151422459535032?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"2d95285af2acda7da0dfebd93f0ec23d0920bdaf","tid":1754591,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/frown_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/angry_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" clas